high_descs: take the tomato from the fridge
take the tomato to the sink
wash it in the sink then remove
take the tomato to the counter to the right of the sink
put the tomato on the counter
anns.task_desc: wash a tomato and put it on the counter

high_descs: Walk to the wall then turn left to face the fridge.
Take a tomato from the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink on the left, wash it off, and pick it up.
Turn right and walk to the microwave.
Put the tomato down on the counter next to the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold, clean tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and grab the tomato by the mug then close the door.
Turn left and walk to the sink then take a big step left.
Wash the tomato in the left sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Take a step to your right.
Put the tomato under the sponge to your right.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato on the counter.
